<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Look it has been a weird few years. In Februar=
y 2021, during meme-stock mania, I coined <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/30048191.260538/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9=
