 itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"=
color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px;=
 border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color=
: #ccc;">  the idea that</a>=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cthe way finance=C2=A0works now i=
s that things are valuable not based on their cash flows but on their proxi=
mity to Elon Musk=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Musk is the richest person in the =
world, and in a dynamic, fun, traveling-to-Mars sort of way. It makes sense=
 that his pronouncements have a certain religious character, that his tweet=
s can endow arbitrary=C2=A0objects with=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/30048191.260538/aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3Jn=
L3dpa2kvTWFuYQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB750a65c9" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;"><em>mana</em></a>. If the richest person in the world tweets =
=E2=80=9CGamestonk!=E2=80=9D then I think that means that, if you buy GameS=
top stock, you will partake in his wealth and dynamism at a remove; you wil=
l get rich and have fun doing it. (Not! Investing! Advice!) Maybe that is n=
ot how it works on a conscious level=E2=80=94though I=C2=A0think that somet=
imes it is?=E2=80=94but surely at some subconscious level people want to or=
der their lives in accordance with the cryptic instructions of a charismati=
c flying zillionaire.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Now, uh, things are different? Tesla Inc., Mus=
k=E2=80=99s main company, was worth as much as $1.2=C2=A0trillion at the st=
art of this year; it=E2=80=99s now worth about $440 billion, and Musk is no=
 longer the richest person in the world. One possibility =E2=80=94=C2=A0one=
 that sort of fits within the spirit of the Elon Markets Hypothesis =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0is that Elon Musk no longer seems all that dynamic or fun or even =
interested in traveling to Mars; now he spends all his time moderating a ni=
che internet message board and getting in fights with posters, and absolute=
ly no one aspires to that.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another possibility is that this entire hypoth=
esis was (1) stupid or (2) a low-interest-rates phenomenon. When capital is=
 cheap and plentiful and a dollar in the distant future is worth as much as=
 a dollar today, the guy who promises robot taxis and Mars colonies can eas=
ily create value with a tweet. When it isn=E2=80=99t, he can=E2=80=99t.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On Twitter this weekend, investor Ross Gerber =
complained that Tesla=E2=80=99s stock isn=E2=80=99t doing that well, and <a=
 href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30048191.260538/aHR0=
cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9lbG9ubXVzay9zdGF0dXMvMTYwNTMwMjQzOTE0NTYxOTQ1OA/607f=
07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0c8951a8" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscop=
e" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Musk replied</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Go back and read your old Securities Analysis =
101 textbook</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In simple terms: As bank savings account inter=
est rates, which are guaranteed, start to approach stock market returns, wh=
ich are *not* guaranteed, people will increasingly move their money out of =
stocks into cash, thus causing stocks to drop.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">People quickly <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/30048191.260538/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9xdWFud=
GlhbjEvc3RhdHVzLzE2MDUzMDgwNjEwOTQyMTU2ODI/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB53b993b=
