 by saying:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So the proposition is =E2=80=A6=C2=
=A0what? You take all of your money, you=C2=A0<em>give it to Musk=C2=A0</em=
>to buy equity in his company at a price that you all agree is absurd? And =
then you get to work for him, running a sullen and broken Twitter according=
