o its business in the US in a compliant way. And then it turned out to be s=
tealing customer money, oops. The authorities have been burned. It is much =
less appealing now than it was three months ago for a regulator or congress=
person to take smiling photographs with crypto exchange operators, or to pu=
t out announcements about how they are working with those operators to brin=
g sensible common-sense regulation to crypto.=C2=A0</p>
